cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.SP. 

The paper deals with signal processing and estimation of the number of sources in PCA and MUSIC algorithms, which are commonly used in array signal processing. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing), and cs.SP (Speech Processing) are likely sub-categories. The paper also uses Bayesian methods for estimation, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
